Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:02.21,Def_Top,,0,0,0,,{\an7\pos(90,45)}"The Diary of Andre"
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.17,0:00:04.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Are we sure he is well?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.97,0:00:07.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I tried talking to him,\Nbut he doesn't respond at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.05,0:00:12.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Can this truly happen to a person,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.06,0:00:15.39,Default,,0,0,0,,just for going a week without any punishment?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.39,0:00:17.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Punishment...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.61,0:00:23.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Punishment... Punishment...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.65,0:00:26.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Be back by suppertime at 6:30.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.95,0:00:29.87,Default,,0,0,0,,If you don't come back,\Nit will be considered a breakout.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.87,0:00:31.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.37,0:00:33.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I haven't exactly done that much lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.79,0:00:36.41,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong with you?\NDon't you want to go out?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.41,0:00:39.33,Default,,0,0,0,,No! I will be glad to go out!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.09,0:00:43.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Punishment...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.76,0:00:45.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Poor Andre.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.72,0:00:49.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Why is Andre the only one the\Nvice president isn't punishing?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.14,0:00:52.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to say, there have been\Ntoo many strange happenings lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.52,0:00:54.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Shingo...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.68,0:00:57.31,Default,,0,0,0,,What?! Don't suddenly shout at me like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.31,0:00:58.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh... Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.98,0:01:03.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen, you've been in a lot\Nwith the vice president lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.11,0:01:03.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Is everything okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.90,0:01:06.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.11,0:01:09.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, as long as she's not\Ndoing anything to you, okay, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.11,0:01:12.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Lately, the Underground Student Council\Nhas been acting strangely.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.91,0:01:17.00,Default,,0,0,0,,So I was thinking, if they were\Ndoing something to you, let me know.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.00,0:01:19.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like to help.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.12,0:01:21.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Shingo! Come to the Corrections Office!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.50,0:01:22.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.71,0:01:28.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I can be back by 6:30 with time to spare.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.17,0:01:29.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.26,0:01:31.05,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you staring off into space about?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.05,0:01:32.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.68,0:01:34.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold mine, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.89,0:01:36.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me, coming through.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.81,0:01:40.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Holy crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.23,0:01:42.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't wait to see these "Grapes of Wrath."
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.52,0:01:46.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I know. I wonder how the\Ngrapes are gonna attack people.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.65,0:01:49.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, you're freaking out, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.15,0:01:51.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not freaking out!\NIf anyone, Anzu, {\i1}you{\i0} are--
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.36,0:01:52.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Shh! It's starting.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.91,0:01:57.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Today, starting now, I want you\Nto service the barricade's entrance!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.45,0:02:00.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, carrying on your club's\Nactivities out here, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.33,0:02:04.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, mm-hmm. The weather's nice today,\Nso we're playing outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.38,0:02:07.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice and refined, isn't it? Well then...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.05,0:02:08.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.05,0:02:16.01,Def_Top,,0,0,0,,"Boys expelled today"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.18,0:02:18.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this really that badly put-together?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.85,0:02:23.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Is Andre-{\i1}dono{\i0} not going\Nto shower again today?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.19,0:02:25.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Nope. I tried talking to him,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.48,0:02:28.32,Default,,0,0,0,,but he's sitting in the corner of his room again.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.32,0:02:31.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I was so nervous the vice\Npresident would find out.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.24,0:02:34.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks for your help, Mayumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.20,0:02:36.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you think your message got through?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.49,0:02:40.12,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all right. Just for a second,\Nwhen we made eye contact,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.12,0:02:41.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I sensed a response from him.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.54,0:02:45.33,Def_Top,,0,0,0,,"Takida Iyon Gaushi Ku."
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.54,0:02:45.67,Default,,0,0,0,,"Takida Iyon Gaushi Ku..."
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.67,0:02:47.67,Default,,0,0,0,,What on earth does it mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.67,0:02:51.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Punishment... Whipping... Spitting...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.22,0:02:52.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Punishment...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.26,0:02:55.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Andre...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.22,0:02:57.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Punishment time...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.89,0:03:00.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Andre...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.48,0:03:03.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Punishment time...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.40,0:03:06.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Andre...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.51,0:03:29.09,Def_Ita,,0,0,0,,Da-da-da-da, dare to escape
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.09,0:03:31.60,Def_Ita,,0,0,0,,Ge-ge-ge-ge, let's get away
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.60,0:03:33.68,Def_Ita,,0,0,0,,Zun-zun-zun-zun, prison, prison
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.68,0:03:36.60,Def_Ita,,0,0,0,,Reach out and grab your freedom
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.60,0:03:39.06,Def_Ita,,0,0,0,,A-na-na-na, dig a tunnel
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.06,0:03:41.61,Def_Ita,,0,0,0,,Jai-jai-jai-jai jailbreak
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.61,0:03:43.77,Def_Ita,,0,0,0,,Zun-zun-zun-zun, prison, prison
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.78,0:03:46.61,Def_Ita,,0,0,0,,Get out from under their rule
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.61,0:03:49.11,Def_Ita,,0,0,0,,(Judge) What can you do
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.11,0:03:51.57,Def_Ita,,0,0,0,,(Innocent) once you get free?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.58,0:03:54.16,Def_Ita,,0,0,0,,(Judge) I can be in love
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.16,0:03:56.75,Def_Ita,,0,0,0,,(Guilty) with the one I adore
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.75,0:03:59.08,Def_Ita,,0,0,0,,(Prison) But once you're in love
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.08,0:04:01.75,Def_Ita,,0,0,0,,(Breakout) you bind and are bound
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.75,0:04:04.00,Def_Ita,,0,0,0,,You wind up a warden
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.00,0:04:07.13,Def_Ita,,0,0,0,,Ah, it's a prison
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.13,0:04:09.43,Def_Ita,,0,0,0,,Pri-Prison, a prison of love
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.43,0:04:11.89,Def_Ita,,0,0,0,,I want to escape, except
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.93,0:04:14.35,Def_Ita,,0,0,0,,Pri-Prison, a prison of love
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.35,0:04:17.06,Def_Ita,,0,0,0,,there is no escape
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.06,0:04:19.48,Def_Ita,,0,0,0,,Pri-Prison, a prison of love
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.48,0:04:21.85,Def_Ita,,0,0,0,,No matter how far you run
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.86,0:04:27.07,Def_Ita,,0,0,0,,the world is a boundless love--
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.07,0:04:31.45,Def_Ita,,0,0,0,,the heart is an endless love--
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.45,0:04:32.49,Def_Ita,,0,0,0,,--prison
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.78,0:04:53.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, isn't this movie dull?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.95,0:04:54.58,Def_Top,,0,0,0,,{\an9\pos(1170,45)}"No, they're not a penny."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.58,0:04:55.95,Def_Top,,0,0,0,,{\an9\pos(1170,45)}"It's five cents for one."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.32,0:04:55.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, uh, yeah, it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.86,0:04:57.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's get out of here, already.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.24,0:05:02.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, you've still got time, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.41,0:05:03.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.83,0:05:05.42,Default,,0,0,0,,A little more than an hour.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.42,0:05:06.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Where should we go?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.83,0:05:08.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's find a store. My treat.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.96,0:05:11.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, that's okay. Don't overdo it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.42,0:05:14.51,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a park over there. Let's head on over.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.51,0:05:24.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Andre... Punishment time...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.60,0:05:26.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Madam Vice President...!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.52,0:05:29.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Please punish me, Madam Vice President!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.78,0:05:33.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Aw, man...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.04,0:05:45.04,Def_Top,,0,0,0,,"My Slave Diary"\N"Andou Reiji"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.08,0:05:46.33,Default,,0,0,0,,What is my diary doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.92,0:05:51.09,Default,,0,0,0,,"I was in the corner of the room,\Nfeeling sorry for myself as usual,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.09,0:05:55.01,Default,,0,0,0,,when I heard a voice from out of\Nnowhere saying 'Punishment time.'
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.01,0:05:56.72,Default,,0,0,0,,After I followed the voice,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.72,0:05:59.68,Default,,0,0,0,,all I found was a stand-up cutout of the\Nvice president, and I was disappointed."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.68,0:06:02.72,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what just barely happened...!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.72,0:06:06.68,Default,,0,0,0,,"The door inside the Corrections Office\Nwas open, and beyond the door
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.40,0:06:11.61,Def_Top,,0,0,0,,{\an7\pos(90,45)}"Who are you calling mom?\NWho are you calling mom?"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.69,0:06:08.69,Default,,0,0,0,,was the vice president!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.69,0:06:11.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I was finally able to get plenty of punishment."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.69,0:06:17.57,Default,,0,0,0,,If I go... through that door...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.28,0:06:20.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Kiyoshi-{\i1}dono{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.20,0:06:22.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Is something troubling you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.41,0:06:26.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen, does "Takida Iyon\NGaushi Ku" mean anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.16,0:06:31.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? What is that? A spell to raise the dead?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.00,0:06:33.38,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it was written like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.76,0:06:37.63,Default,,0,0,0,,What an ominous missive!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.63,0:06:38.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.59,0:06:40.72,Default,,0,0,0,,You read it top-to-bottom!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.72,0:06:44.35,Default,,0,0,0,,"Boys expelled today"...!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.35,0:06:46.43,Default,,0,0,0,,What does that mean, "expelled"?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.43,0:06:49.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Why would that idea sprout up all of a sudden?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.31,0:06:52.86,Default,,0,0,0,,It may have to do with the strange\Noccurrences happening around us lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.86,0:06:57.32,Default,,0,0,0,,If they were all set up in order\Nto drive us out of school...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.32,0:06:58.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Set up by who?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.57,0:07:00.74,Default,,0,0,0,,It could only be the\NUnderground Student Council!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.82,0:07:03.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Andre!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.03,0:07:07.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! It's the real vice president!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.50,0:07:09.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Andre!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.50,0:07:11.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Kiyoshi-{\i1}dono{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.42,0:07:12.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Over hither!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.13,0:07:21.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you calling your mother?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.26,0:07:22.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.47,0:07:28.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Andre, you're going to need
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.18,0:07:31.64,Default,,0,0,0,,some severe punishing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.65,0:07:34.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom-- I mean, Madam Vice President!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.90,0:07:38.61,Default,,0,0,0,,You "accidentally" called me "Mom" again?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.61,0:07:42.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Please! Punish me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.32,0:07:44.70,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the matter? I can't reach you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.70,0:07:46.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't punish you this way, can I?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.91,0:07:48.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, what's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.96,0:07:51.21,Default,,0,0,0,,--Andre!\N--Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.21,0:07:52.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.46,0:08:01.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Why you... fat pig!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.59,0:08:04.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.43,0:08:05.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Prison break!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.72,0:08:08.31,Default,,0,0,0,,No way! I didn't break out!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.43,0:08:09.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold still!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.89,0:08:10.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Andre...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.77,0:08:12.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Kiyoshi-{\i1}dono{\i0}, look at this.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.98,0:08:16.06,Default,,0,0,0,,These look like they were cut partway\Nthrough by snippers or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.06,0:08:17.61,Default,,0,0,0,,We've been had!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.61,0:08:19.78,Default,,0,0,0,,The Underground Student Council set us up!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.78,0:08:21.53,Default,,0,0,0,,That went well, didn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.53,0:08:26.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. Imagine, a use such as this\Nfor an overstuffed uniform!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.66,0:08:30.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Winding up Andre, already mentally\Npushed to the brink, to a fever pitch,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.37,0:08:34.67,Default,,0,0,0,,and have him break through\Nthe barricade. Just as you planned.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.67,0:08:37.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Way to endure squeezing\Ninto that tight uniform.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.71,0:08:40.42,Default,,0,0,0,,No, not at all. Now...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.42,0:08:43.34,Default,,0,0,0,,...we just wait for the snitch to return.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.34,0:08:45.93,Default,,0,0,0,,So "The Grapes of Wrath"\Nwasn't a horror movie, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.93,0:08:49.35,Default,,0,0,0,,To be honest, I fell asleep\Nless than 30 minutes into it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.35,0:08:53.18,Default,,0,0,0,,That's too soon! I was straining\Nto stay awake, myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.19,0:08:54.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm super-sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.31,0:08:56.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Man...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.19,0:08:57.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Pinchy-pinchy!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.52,0:09:00.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so happy! I'm beyond happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.94,0:09:05.03,Default,,0,0,0,,And, the way things are headed,\NI might score even more happiness...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.03,0:09:06.78,Default,,0,0,0,,...meaning...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.78,0:09:08.87,Default,,0,0,0,,...I might land a kiss, here...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.87,0:09:09.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Yikes!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.74,0:09:10.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.41,0:09:14.50,Default,,0,0,0,,What, are you angry? You just\Ngave me an awfully creepy look.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.50,0:09:18.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I ain't mad! In fact, I'm super-happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.25,0:09:19.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? You're happy?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.63,0:09:21.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Er, no...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.00,0:09:23.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Why would you make a face\Nlike that when you're happy?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.55,0:09:26.30,Default,,0,0,0,,You pinch cheeks, and that's the face it makes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.30,0:09:28.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.14,0:09:30.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, you pinch {\i1}my{\i0} cheeks, and let's see.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.35,0:09:31.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.97,0:09:35.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Well? Do I look creepy?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.44,0:09:39.56,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Say something!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.62,0:09:54.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, I can't watch anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.29,0:09:56.54,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you throwing sand at him for?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.54,0:09:58.37,Default,,0,0,0,,It could get into his eyes, you know!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.38,0:10:00.84,Default,,0,0,0,,That's okay! I mean, it's his own fault!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.84,0:10:03.50,Default,,0,0,0,,He ditched us and went off to play with a girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.51,0:10:05.67,Default,,0,0,0,,He's allowed to do\Nsomething like that, isn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.67,0:10:09.01,Default,,0,0,0,,No he's not! We made a rule\Nthat says no playing with girls!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.01,0:10:10.05,Default,,0,0,0,,You double-crosser!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.05,0:10:11.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I said stop that!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.27,0:10:18.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah... I'm sorry I yelled at you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.77,0:10:22.48,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's not very manly to\Npick on someone like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.48,0:10:24.61,Default,,0,0,0,,If he's your friend, then forgive him.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.94,0:10:26.86,Default,,0,0,0,,What was that for?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.86,0:10:28.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't bully the others!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.82,0:10:29.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go, guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.95,0:10:31.37,Default,,0,0,0,,--Yeah!\N--Mm-hmm!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.95,0:10:35.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Children are so capricious, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.04,0:10:37.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Still, it ended up working out, didn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.54,0:10:39.54,Default,,0,0,0,,It looks like they made up, and everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.54,0:10:43.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Shingo, way to be watching out.\NThat was pretty cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.09,0:10:47.51,Default,,0,0,0,,If he's your friend...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.26,0:10:51.39,Default,,0,0,0,,...then forgive him, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.35,0:10:56.31,Default,,0,0,0,,And after I didn't forgive him one bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.31,0:10:59.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? What is it? What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.27,0:11:01.31,Default,,0,0,0,,The truth is,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.31,0:11:03.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been allowed\Nto go outside in return
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.86,0:11:06.98,Default,,0,0,0,,for spilling information on\Nthe others to the vice president!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.99,0:11:11.49,Default,,0,0,0,,They're all doing prison labor,\Nwhile I've been going to the game center,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.49,0:11:15.41,Default,,0,0,0,,and fooling around with you. I suck.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.41,0:11:17.58,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a full-blown breakout.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.58,0:11:19.75,Default,,0,0,0,,You guys lured him out, didn't you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.75,0:11:21.75,Default,,0,0,0,,You all saw him, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.75,0:11:24.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Andre came out all on his own.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.50,0:11:26.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Guys, I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.59,0:11:30.01,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the second breakout, following Kiyoshi's.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.01,0:11:31.88,Default,,0,0,0,,According to the\NUnderground Student Council rules,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.89,0:11:35.68,Default,,0,0,0,,your sentences are to be\Nextended for three more months.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.68,0:11:38.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry to bore you will all of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.18,0:11:40.35,Default,,0,0,0,,It's still early, but I'm\Nheading back to the school.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.35,0:11:42.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to apologize to everyone,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.40,0:11:44.86,Default,,0,0,0,,and I don't want to\Nembarrass myself any further.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.32,0:11:48.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry... Shingo...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.63,0:11:56.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I've... done something I have to\Napologize to you for, Shingo.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.72,0:11:58.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.01,0:11:59.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Come to think of it, where's Shingo?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.80,0:12:04.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I told him to be back by 6:30,\Nbut he's taking his time coming back.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.14,0:12:07.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I told him that if he's one\Nminute-- one {\i1}second{\i0} late,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.23,0:12:08.85,Default,,0,0,0,,it counts as a breakout.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.85,0:12:11.69,Default,,0,0,0,,You mean, you set a trap for Shingo, too?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.69,0:12:14.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Where on earth could he be traipsing around?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.90,0:12:18.03,Def_Top,,0,0,0,,"Underground Student Council\NCaptain of the Guard"\N"Yokoyama Anzu"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.45,0:12:19.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you content with your current position?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.24,0:12:22.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yes, ma'am. I am greatly honored to be able
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.28,0:12:26.45,Default,,0,0,0,,to support the Underground\NStudent Council as captain of the guard.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.46,0:12:30.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Anzu-{\i1}san{\i0}, are you interested in\Nan executive post next term?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.88,0:12:32.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, but I couldn't...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.59,0:12:35.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Anzu-{\i1}san{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.21,0:12:39.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a certain task I'd like you to do.\NIf you are successful...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.85,0:12:44.18,Default,,0,0,0,,...I will recommend you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.18,0:12:48.98,Default,,0,0,0,,And so, I was told to get friendly\Nwith you outside of school.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.98,0:12:51.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you... serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.23,0:12:53.94,Default,,0,0,0,,It was all for today.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.94,0:12:56.15,Default,,0,0,0,,If I kept you here, Shingo,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.15,0:12:59.49,Default,,0,0,0,,and made sure you didn't get\Nback to the school in time,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.49,0:13:01.91,Default,,0,0,0,,the boys would commit a third breakout,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.91,0:13:03.32,Default,,0,0,0,,and all of you will be expelled!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.33,0:13:04.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Expelled?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.12,0:13:07.95,Default,,0,0,0,,The Underground Student Council set you up.\NThere's no time! Get back, quickly!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.96,0:13:11.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not sure I get all of it, but all right!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.00,0:13:12.08,Default,,0,0,0,,There's plenty of time if I run back--
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.08,0:13:14.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You're wrong! That's 30 minutes slow!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.50,0:13:16.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I set it back at the movie theater!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.76,0:13:18.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Then, right now, it's...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.72,0:13:22.59,Default,,0,0,0,,6:25.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.59,0:13:25.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Only five minutes. There is not enough time!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.89,0:13:27.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.02,0:13:28.68,Default,,0,0,0,,We're done for.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.68,0:13:31.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure he'll be here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.35,0:13:33.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure Shingo will be back in time.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.86,0:13:34.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Based on what?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.86,0:13:36.40,Default,,0,0,0,,All we can do is hope, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.40,0:13:39.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Hope... and wait for Shingo.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.24,0:13:46.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Four more minutes, now,\Nuntil you are all expelled.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.16,0:13:48.24,Default,,0,0,0,,What a shame, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.25,0:13:50.62,Default,,0,0,0,,During the summer, there's seaside school,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.62,0:13:53.21,Default,,0,0,0,,where we have campfires and barbecue,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.21,0:13:55.29,Default,,0,0,0,,and hold a wet T-shirt contest,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.29,0:13:56.54,Default,,0,0,0,,and other wall-to-wall fun events.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.55,0:13:57.59,Default,,0,0,0,,--Wet...\N--...T-shirt...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.59,0:13:59.01,Default,,0,0,0,,--...contes--\N--...t?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.67,0:14:03.72,Default,,0,0,0,,No, Shingo-{\i1}kun{\i0} is sure to make it back.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.72,0:14:05.22,Default,,0,0,0,,All we can do is believe.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.22,0:14:06.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I believe!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.10,0:14:09.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Guys, reach out to him, with our hopes!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.60,0:14:12.39,Default,,0,0,0,,--Shingo! Come back!\N--Shingo! Get back here!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.39,0:14:14.15,Default,,0,0,0,,--Come home!\N--Shingo!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.77,0:14:16.56,Def_Top,,0,0,0,,"Shirukuma Cleaning"
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.40,0:14:21.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Shingo!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.32,0:14:25.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop shouting! Be quiet!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.07,0:14:28.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Shingo-{\i1}dono{\i0}! Come home!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.54,0:14:30.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Why, you...!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.25,0:14:33.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Madam Vice President,\Nlet them have their way.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.17,0:14:35.00,Default,,0,0,0,,As long as Anzu keeps him there,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.00,0:14:37.50,Default,,0,0,0,,the snitch will not be coming back.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.50,0:14:39.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, are you okay?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.17,0:14:43.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I'm all right. I just fell down;\Nyou didn't hit me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.59,0:14:45.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Never mind me, what time is it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.85,0:14:51.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Scream! Scream! Scream away!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.85,0:14:57.10,Default,,0,0,0,,One more minute, and we will get\Nour peaceful school life back.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.23,0:15:01.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks, Pops!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.19,0:15:02.03,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Shingo!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.03,0:15:02.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Shingo-{\i1}kun{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.94,0:15:04.36,Default,,0,0,0,,He finally got here, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.36,0:15:06.99,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the old gent from the cleaners!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.99,0:15:07.66,Default,,0,0,0,,How...?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.66,0:15:09.08,Default,,0,0,0,,--Shingo, hurry!\N--Shingo-{\i1}kun{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.08,0:15:10.41,Default,,0,0,0,,There is no time!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.41,0:15:11.45,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the time?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.45,0:15:12.54,Default,,0,0,0,,30 more seconds!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.54,0:15:14.46,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay! He's gonna make it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.46,0:15:15.96,Default,,0,0,0,,--He did it!\N--Shingo-{\i1}kun{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.96,0:15:16.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.38,0:15:17.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Ten seconds left.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.67,0:15:19.50,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you waiting for?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.50,0:15:20.34,Default,,0,0,0,,--Hurry and open it!\N--Five...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.34,0:15:21.50,Default,,0,0,0,,--I know! But something's--\N--Four...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.51,0:15:22.38,Default,,0,0,0,,--It won't open!\N--Three...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.38,0:15:23.71,Default,,0,0,0,,--Shingo, no!\N--Two...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.72,0:15:25.13,Default,,0,0,0,,--The door is--\N--One...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.39,0:15:30.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Zero.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.60,0:15:32.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Time over.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.89,0:15:37.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Screw that! It's not fair if it's locked!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.52,0:15:41.98,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?\NThe door opens like this, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.98,0:15:44.82,Default,,0,0,0,,No way... When did it...?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.82,0:15:46.86,Default,,0,0,0,,It was badly put-together, you see.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.86,0:15:49.03,Default,,0,0,0,,They fixed it for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.03,0:15:51.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn, so {\i1}that's{\i0} what that was about!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.50,0:15:55.91,Default,,0,0,0,,That makes it your third breakout.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.91,0:15:59.38,Default,,0,0,0,,As such, you will all be expelled.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.38,0:16:02.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you hear? The boys broke out\Ntwice yesterday alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.67,0:16:04.63,Default,,0,0,0,,That means they're expelled, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.63,0:16:07.55,Default,,0,0,0,,It will be a relief not having\Nthose nasty boys around.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.59,0:16:10.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Shingo...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.26,0:16:11.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.60,0:16:14.68,Default,,0,0,0,,You were seeing a girl outside of the school?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.68,0:16:18.48,Default,,0,0,0,,After you ragged on Kiyoshi\Nover seeing a girl, too, Shingo.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.48,0:16:23.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Not to mention that the girl was a kunoichi put\Nup to it by the Underground Student Council.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.94,0:16:29.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I really am sorry. Guys, you can\Nbeat me until you're satisfied. Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.70,0:16:33.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Stand up, Shingo.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.70,0:16:39.62,Default,,0,0,0,,When my breakout was discovered,\Nyou hit me, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.62,0:16:40.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Kiyoshi-{\i1}dono{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.54,0:16:43.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. Hit me as hard as you like.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.34,0:16:45.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, don't mind if I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.47,0:16:52.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Now we're even.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.35,0:16:53.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Kiyoshi...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.10,0:17:01.77,Default,,0,0,0,,We're all equally guilty.\NNo one here could hit you for real.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.77,0:17:05.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Verily. Shingo-{\i1}dono{\i0}, you were just set up\Nby the Underground Student Council,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.98,0:17:09.07,Default,,0,0,0,,and had your manly feelings toyed around with.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.07,0:17:10.91,Default,,0,0,0,,If anything, we feel sorry for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.91,0:17:14.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Shingo-{\i1}kun{\i0}, you apologized.\NThat's good enough for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.74,0:17:18.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, Kiyoshi does have a point.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.16,0:17:19.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.17,0:17:25.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I did all those terrible things...\NThings that betrayed you...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.63,0:17:28.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, guys...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.13,0:17:33.43,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, Shingo-{\i1}dono{\i0},\Nwhen you were rushing back full-tilt,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.43,0:17:35.51,Default,,0,0,0,,yours truly was quite moved.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.51,0:17:39.68,Default,,0,0,0,,It's because Anzu told me\Nthat I got back by the time I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.06,0:17:43.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Ho... "Anzu"?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.48,0:17:46.57,Default,,0,0,0,,You are already on terms close enough\Nnot to warrant name suffixes?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.57,0:17:51.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, well... we hold hands, and pinch\Neach other's cheeks, and stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.57,0:17:55.07,Default,,0,0,0,,You did all {\i1}that{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.08,0:17:58.66,Default,,0,0,0,,But it was all part of her trap,\Nso you couldn't help it, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.66,0:18:00.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I guess so.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.37,0:18:05.13,Default,,0,0,0,,The downblouse and nip-slip might\Nalso have been part of the trap, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.13,0:18:08.38,Default,,0,0,0,,But in the end, she told me\Nthe truth about everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.38,0:18:11.67,Default,,0,0,0,,So I feel like I really\Nshared something with Anzu.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.64,0:18:20.56,Default,,0,0,0,,You said you wouldn't hit me for real...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.56,0:18:23.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Your crime in seeing nipples is too serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.44,0:18:27.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Indeed it is. Though you did see nipples as part\Nof the Underground Student Council's setup,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.36,0:18:29.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I am contrarily much too envious.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.36,0:18:32.65,Default,,0,0,0,,If you saw nipples, then just\Napologizing is not good enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.65,0:18:34.86,Default,,0,0,0,,You saw nipples, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.86,0:18:36.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Now we really are even.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.24,0:18:40.16,Def_Top,,0,0,0,,"School Council Chairman's Office"
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.54,0:18:42.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Gentlemen, I'm pleased to meet...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.87,0:18:44.21,Default,,0,0,0,,...you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.21,0:18:45.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Pleased to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.71,0:18:49.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I did not expect that we should\Nhave to meet like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.17,0:18:51.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You know the reason why you were\Ncalled in here today...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.97,0:18:52.34,Default,,0,0,0,,...right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.34,0:18:54.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Sister set them up!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.26,0:18:56.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Chiyo, I will listen to what\Nyou have to say after--
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.18,0:18:58.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I saw it in the Underground\NStudent Council room!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.81,0:19:02.60,Default,,0,0,0,,A document with "DTO: Danshi Taigaku\NOperation" written on it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.60,0:19:05.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Mari, is what she's saying...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.27,0:19:05.60,Default,,0,0,0,,...true?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.60,0:19:07.52,Default,,0,0,0,,She must be mistaken.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.52,0:19:10.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I have never seen nor heard of such a thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.36,0:19:14.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Without any proof,\Nno explanation is warranted.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.11,0:19:17.16,Default,,0,0,0,,If that's all you have to say,\Nrun along, Chiyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.66,0:19:22.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry I couldn't be\Nany help, Kiyoshi-{\i1}kun{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.08,0:19:23.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Chiyo-{\i1}chan{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.87,0:19:28.54,Default,,0,0,0,,In accordance with Underground Student\NCouncil regulations, you are to be expelled.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.54,0:19:29.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that right, Chairman?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.88,0:19:33.13,Default,,0,0,0,,According to the regulations...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.13,0:19:34.67,Default,,0,0,0,,...yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.67,0:19:37.68,Default,,0,0,0,,This matter will be discussed at\Nnext week's committee meeting,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.68,0:19:43.06,Default,,0,0,0,,which will end with the chairman affixing\Nhis seal to the expulsion papers, finalizing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.06,0:19:45.18,Default,,0,0,0,,When are you planning to affix your seal?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.44,0:19:51.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Chairman! Rules are rules!\NWhen will you affix your seal?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.23,0:19:57.07,Default,,0,0,0,,The end of the week after next, at the latest.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.07,0:20:00.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, DTO really worked, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.03,0:20:01.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Masterfully carried out, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.87,0:20:06.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, a toast. To the boys leaving the school.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.54,0:20:08.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Cheers!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.25,0:20:11.96,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, in celebration of\Nthe great success of DTO,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.96,0:20:14.00,Default,,0,0,0,,if I may be so bold, a little performance...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.26,0:20:19.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Watch as I do 50 pull-ups\Nusing only my fingers.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.18,0:20:23.97,Default,,0,0,0,,One... two...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.97,0:20:28.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Come to think of it, how did Shingo\Nmake it back by curfew, anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.02,0:20:32.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I will call Anzu in and\Nask her about that matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.23,0:20:34.32,Default,,0,0,0,,...forty-seven...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.32,0:20:35.61,Default,,0,0,0,,...forty-eight...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.61,0:20:37.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Only two more to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.28,0:20:38.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Hang in there, Madam Vice President!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.91,0:20:40.57,Default,,0,0,0,,You're almost there!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.57,0:20:41.99,Default,,0,0,0,,...forty-nine...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.66,0:20:46.54,Default,,0,0,0,,...fifty--
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.79,0:20:48.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Please excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.33,0:20:53.17,Default,,0,0,0,,The end of the week after next,\Nwe shall be expelled from school.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.84,0:20:56.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Wet T-shirt contest, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.72,0:20:59.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Wet T-shirt contest?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.76,0:21:02.64,Default,,0,0,0,,You mean when girls in T-shirts\Nget splashed with water?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.64,0:21:05.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. Apparently, they do that\Nduring seaside school.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.43,0:21:10.77,Default,,0,0,0,,For a moment, on my way back to the school,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.77,0:21:14.23,Default,,0,0,0,,the image of a wet T-shirt\Ncontest flashed through my mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.23,0:21:17.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought to myself,\N"What was that?" so I turned around,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.32,0:21:19.28,Default,,0,0,0,,and this van was coming...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.28,0:21:23.41,Default,,0,0,0,,If it hadn't been for that,\NI'd probably have been run over.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.41,0:21:27.45,Default,,0,0,0,,What?! To think that our hopes\Nreally did reach you...!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.45,0:21:28.91,Default,,0,0,0,,It is a miracle!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.91,0:21:30.79,Default,,0,0,0,,You mean it? That's awesome.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.79,0:21:33.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Miracles {\i1}do{\i0} happen, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.13,0:21:37.17,Default,,0,0,0,,So you became taken with Shingo,\Nand told him the truth?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.17,0:21:41.18,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the captain of the guard;\Nwhat were you thinking?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.18,0:21:43.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm terribly sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.68,0:21:44.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, no matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.89,0:21:46.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.06,0:21:48.81,Default,,0,0,0,,DTO still ended up being successful.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.81,0:21:50.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I shall not press you any further.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.64,0:21:51.94,Default,,0,0,0,,No, but I--
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.94,0:21:55.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I said it was all right. Go on.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.27,0:21:56.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.15,0:21:58.07,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have to shut the door.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.07,0:22:01.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, Madam Vice President, please excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.20,0:22:03.61,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay. Go.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.61,0:22:05.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you sure, Madam President?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.70,0:22:10.00,Default,,0,0,0,,She knows about DTO. She should\Nprobably be kept under observation
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.00,0:22:11.58,Default,,0,0,0,,until the boys are expelled.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.58,0:22:15.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Indeed. Leave it to you, Madam\NPresident, to consider that.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.88,0:22:18.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Madam Vice President, are you\Nsure you don't need a hand?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.34,0:22:21.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm fine. I can get out of this by myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.72,0:22:23.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Hang in there, Madam Vice President.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.38,0:22:24.97,Default,,0,0,0,,You're almost there, Madam Vice President.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.22,0:22:28.22,Default,,0,0,0,,My fingertips have no strength left.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.22,0:22:29.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll just have to...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.27,0:22:37.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Miracles don't happen by waiting around.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.36,0:22:39.65,Default,,0,0,0,,We have to make them happen ourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.65,0:22:42.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Just like we kept Shingo from that accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.36,0:22:46.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Truly, Shingo-{\i1}dono{\i0}'s tale is a miraculous one.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.16,0:22:49.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Are we just going to give up on\Nthat wet T-shirt contest?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.33,0:22:51.66,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no way we can give up!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.66,0:22:53.37,Default,,0,0,0,,But, what are we supposed to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.37,0:22:56.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Chiyo-{\i1}chan{\i0} said there was a\Nproject plan for DTO, didn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.71,0:22:58.08,Default,,0,0,0,,If we can just locate that...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.09,0:23:01.92,Default,,0,0,0,,But that's already been disposed of, hasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.92,0:23:03.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.72,0:23:06.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.18,0:23:09.72,Default,,0,0,0,,...saw "DTO" someplace before...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.81,0:23:28.11,Def_Ita,,0,0,0,,Falling in love with someone is
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.11,0:23:31.45,Def_Ita,,0,0,0,,a trap programmed into our genes
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.45,0:23:36.45,Def_Ita,,0,0,0,,Our desires have already gotten underway
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.33,0:23:41.54,Def_Ita,,0,0,0,,Lots of things happen day to day
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.54,0:23:44.96,Def_Ita,,0,0,0,,Lots of things happen in innocence
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.96,0:23:51.72,Def_Ita,,0,0,0,,They wrench our hearts as we grapple with them
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.72,0:23:55.01,Def_Ita,,0,0,0,,Don't you touch, let me touch your heart
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.01,0:23:58.39,Def_Ita,,0,0,0,,Pry it open and punish me even more
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.39,0:24:03.69,Def_Ita,,0,0,0,,With all our minds, we submissively fall in love
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.69,0:24:05.31,Def_Ita,,0,0,0,,Love & Peace, Fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.31,0:24:08.57,Def_Ita,,0,0,0,,We want to have you
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.57,0:24:12.11,Def_Ita,,0,0,0,,We want to know everything
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.11,0:24:18.83,Def_Ita,,0,0,0,,Grant us permission for our dreams
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.83,0:24:22.12,Def_Ita,,0,0,0,,We don't need any love
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.12,0:24:25.54,Def_Ita,,0,0,0,,On second thought, give us some
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.54,0:24:31.76,Def_Ita,,0,0,0,,You can't put handcuffs on adolescence
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.51,0:24:48.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Next time on Prison School:
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.64,0:24:49.98,Default,,0,0,0,,"Full of Bodily Fluids"
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.77,0:24:49.98,Def_Top,,0,0,0,,"Full of Bodily Fluids"
